573
00:28:33,051 --> 00:28:34,731
She reminds me of my parents.

574
00:28:35,731 --> 00:28:38,130
I used to hate my father
all these years.

575
00:28:38,771 --> 00:28:39,650
But after meeting

576
00:28:39,971 --> 00:28:41,691
Miss Song Yun,

577
