out of no reason,

578
00:28:44,650 --> 00:28:45,531
I started to ponder

579
00:28:46,810 --> 00:28:47,971
what dire situation

580
00:28:48,971 --> 00:28:50,610
my mother might face

581
00:28:51,931 --> 00:28:53,291
and how she would live on

582
